verbose_text: M1 and M2 were separately cultured either in control, B16F10 derived or A-549-derived tumoral media for 24 h. M1 showed a significant increase of SPARC and TyrRS expression both at mRNA (XREF_FIG A, B) and protein levels when cultured in tumor conditioned medium, compared to M2 (XREF_FIG C-N, M1 protein levels quantified in XREF_FIG O).
